# Market Trading & Algorithmic Signals

This collection focuses on **Analyzing market data to generate trading signals, forecast volatility, and model yield curves.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_stock_price_volatility_forecasting.ipynb
- 02_etf_arbitrage_signal_detection.ipynb
- 03_news_sentiment_trading_signals.ipynb
- 04_limit_order_book_liquidity_prediction.ipynb
- 05_cryptocurrency_price_spike_detection.ipynb
- 06_yield_curve_forecasting_pca.ipynb
